Citigroup Commercial Mortgage Bond Trading Head Warren Geiger Leaves Firm

-- B y   S a r a h   M u l h o l l a n d   a n d   D o n a l   G r i f f i n
-- 
2011-07-28T17:58:42Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-28/citigroup-commercial-mortgage-bond-trading-head-warren-geiger-leaves-firm.html
Warren Geiger, who headed commercial
mortgage bond trading at  Citigroup Inc. (C) , has left the bank,
according to an e-mailed statement.  Geiger’s departure is unrelated to a review by Standard &
Poor’s of its ratings on a commercial mortgage bond offering
from Citigroup and  Goldman Sachs Group Inc. (GS) , Danielle Romero-
Apsilos, a spokewoman for Citigroup, said today in an e-mailed
statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Sarah Mulholland in New York at 
 smulholland3@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alan Goldstein at 
 agoldstein5@bloomberg.net  